{"tid":756792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔單挑？  大陸仔表演生吞老鼠頭(慎入)","createTime":"2018-07-26T09:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T11:16:03.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d58532a45558c1e43eed42faa1144979609791df","tid":756792,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"曾經在網上聽人說過，沒有把元素周期表都吃過，就不要稱自己做中國人，一方面反映內地食品安全問題，另一方面顯示內地人大部分東西都能吃的「傳統」，不過說到生食老鼠頭，相信就不是人人都夠膽了。最近網上流傳一段影片，一名男子於鏡頭面前示範食死老鼠，噁心指數爆燈。<br />\n<br />\n內地網絡紅人「旋瘋歐巴」日前分享一段影片，他在鏡頭前拿著一隻死老鼠，並轉動老鼠證明這隻是千真萬確的死老鼠後，直接張大嘴咬扯老鼠的頭部，直至傳出清脆的「卡」一聲，老鼠的頭被扯出，「旋瘋歐巴」直接在嘴巴咀嚼，他又多次強調這隻是老鼠而非倉鼠或其他生物，非常噁心和恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180726/1/67/1/玩命-為搏點擊率-內地網紅生吞老鼠頭-9069927.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%E7%8E%A9%E5%91%BD-%E7%82%BA%E6%90%8F%E9%BB%9E%E6%93%8A%E7%8E%87-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E7%94%9F%E5%90%9E%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E9%A0%AD-9069927.html&d=MS5Lvb1G68LAnWEss6f3Jdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c2e1b89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180726/1/67/1/玩命-為搏點擊率-內地網紅生吞老鼠頭-9069927.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/07/26/9/994359fdff74a5b632ef3fb48b11ce55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F9%2F994359fdff74a5b632ef3fb48b11ce55.jpg&h=e65c85b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/07/26/0/063843b558908e37df45139e116a26bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F0%2F063843b558908e37df45139e116a26bc.jpg&h=ade3420c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/07/26/1/1ad093f8d92a3fd5d0d27ec38f55980e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F1%2F1ad093f8d92a3fd5d0d27ec